data.description: Welcome to your Homestead Oasis! This charming and spacious home is nestled on 9 acres of gorgeous landscape, complete with a pond for fishing, a barn with stables, an oversized detached 2 car garage with large workshop and a she shed. There is fencing throughout the property and a separate area with a chicken coup. There are garden beds and plenty of space for anyone's gardening dreams. This property is truly a slice of heaven, tucked away from neighbors and well landscaped. The home is not far from the lake and about 20 mins to 811.
